column2: b'Naruto Soyokazeden Movie: Naruto to Mashin to Mitsu no Onegai Dattebayo!!'

b'While enjoying a barbecue alongside team members and peers, Naruto Uzumaki stumbles upon a strange old bottle that houses a genie! The mythical being is willing to grant three wishes, but in a flurry of excitement, Naruto ends up wasting the first two. Outraged, Sasuke Uchiha and Sakura Haruno start fighting with him over the last remaining chance.

As the other ninjas join the dispute, the whole matter\xe2\x80\x94before they know it\xe2\x80\x94turns into an all-out brawl for the precious container.

[Written by MAL Rewrite]'
